data.description: This Southern Colonial brick style two story home was built in 1988 and is located on a 1.13 city corner lot. The four sided brick home in its grandeur has low maintenance in mind with vinyl eaves and soffits to let homeowner spend less time working and more time enjoying. This spacious home has 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths and a half bath within this 4692 sq ft home. The master bedroom is on the main level. The upstairs has a four bedrooms one on each corner and a Jack and Jill bathroom is shared between bedrooms. The spacious bonus room, located in the center of the second floor, has many options. The back yard is fenced in for privacy to enjoy the in-ground pool and open back deck, with pergola, a garden area and a chicken coop. The four sided brick home with a detached brick double garage 28x28, with garage doors and a paved circular driveway. To complete this home and shave some cost from monthly utilities are 2 tankless hot water. Call Vickie Bateman 912-253-0268
